    <item>
      <title>英国养老金行业将支持释放剩余现金的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/uk-pension-industry-would-back-plan-to-unlock-surplus-cash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据报道，英国养老金行业支持政府的计划，即允许企业利用目前锁定在主要员工退休基金中的数十亿英镑盈余。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/uk-pension-industry-would-back-plan-to-unlock-surplus-cash</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 13:08:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普意外发起关税战 引发哥伦比亚股市抛售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/trump-sparks-colombia-selloff-with-unexpected-tariff-spat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于哥伦比亚突然（尽管是短暂的）与其长期政治盟友和最大贸易伙伴美国陷入关税战，哥伦比亚比索大幅下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/trump-sparks-colombia-selloff-with-unexpected-tariff-spat</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 13:06:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度央行采取措施通过购买债券来增加现金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/india-central-bank-takes-steps-to-boost-cash-via-bond-buy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度央行计划向国内金融系统注入近 180 亿美元，加大力度缓解现金短缺问题。印度现金短缺问题达到十多年来的最高水平，一些人认为这损害了亚洲第三大经济体的增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/india-central-bank-takes-steps-to-boost-cash-via-bond-buy</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 12:27:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特斯拉、宝马起诉欧盟 因中国产电动汽车遭关税打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/tesla-bmw-sue-eu-after-china-made-evs-are-hit-by-trade-curbs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克旗下的特斯拉和宝马汽车公司已起诉欧盟执行机构，这是继中国汽车制造商起诉欧盟对进口至欧盟的电动汽车征收高达 45% 的关税之后的又一举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/tesla-bmw-sue-eu-after-china-made-evs-are-hit-by-trade-curbs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 12:15:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普威胁对哥伦比亚征收关税 咖啡价格上涨 供应面临风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/arabica-gains-as-trump-colombia-tariff-threat-shows-supply-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国对哥伦比亚发出短暂的关税威胁之后，阿拉比卡咖啡期货价格创下新高，这加剧了全球供应紧张的市场中的贸易不确定性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/arabica-gains-as-trump-colombia-tariff-threat-shows-supply-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 09:33:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
